<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l28"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewntſchaft</ex></expan> beuor <expan>l<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Morıcʒ vnd <expan>Heınr<ex>ich</ex></expan> als Jr vns nu bey dem <expan>Minn<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l29"><expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır auch wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l30">auf <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>nehſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> / ob eẅch aber <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r2l31"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> niht <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> ſo wıſſet daʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> ıſt / wenn </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_262" id="130r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_262_r1l1">Jr <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſtündt</expan> daʒ dıe ſache Alſo <expan>geſchaff<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> . daʒ man eẅr dort niht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_262_r1l2">bedörft vnd Jr es mıt der von Eger <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> getun möchtet / daʒ Jr </ab>
