<ab facs="#facs_262_r1l8"><expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> form auch <expan>halte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd dargeen <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> Auch ſagt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>freẅnd<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_262_r1l9">dem Rat ʒu Eger / daʒ dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> den wır <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan> Jn den <expan>Salpet<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
