<del rend="strikethrough">bey vns </del> <expan>befelhe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> bey vns ʒu <expan>empfahe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd ʒu Jn ʒu <expan>fertıg<ex>en</ex></expan> / dem </ab>
