<ab facs="#facs_262_r1l13">wo <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der <expan>R<ex>ömiſch</ex></expan> etc künıg yecʒ <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> ſo <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıbt</expan> vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_262_r1l14">das / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſ<ex>ub</ex></expan> ſıgıllo <expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex>ıs</expan> Tucher <expan>ſe<ex>ni</ex><hi rend="sup">orıs</hi></expan> <expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>iſt</ex>rıciuıu<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica</expan> dıe </ab>
