</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_261" id="129v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Moriczen <expan>Awrach<ex>er</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Fronhofer,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dienern</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><app>
<note place="marginleft">In bapiro. </note>
</app><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>ewntschaft</ex></expan> bevor. <expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
                        Moricz und <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns nu bey dem
                                <expan>Minn<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir auch wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        ewch auf <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>nehst<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>, ob ewch aber
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> niht <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, so wisset daz <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> ist, wenn <pb facs="#facs_262" id="130r"/>ir
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>stündt</expan>, daz die sache also
                                <expan>geschaff<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan>, daz man ewr dort niht bedörft und ir es mit
                        der von Eger <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> getun möchtet, daz ir ewch denn,
                        so ir erst möcht, zu uns herheim füget, und daz ir auch die zerung von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> beczalen süllet, in mass als ir gefertigt
                        seyt, es <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> denn, daz ir
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>stündt</expan>, daz es die von Eger von der
                                <expan>zeru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> in arg von uns
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> und <expan>aufneme<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> und daz sie für der von Erffurt und
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stette <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        auch <expan>beczalte<ex>n</ex></expan>, so mugt ir es in
                                <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan> form auch
                            <expan>halte<ex>n</ex></expan> und dargeen
                            <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>. Auch sagt <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan> dem rat zu Eger, daz die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, den wir
                            <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan>, in den <expan>salpet<ex>er</ex></expan> und
                        swefel <expan>zu schik<ex>en</ex></expan>, yecz kein für
                                <expan>gehabe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>muge<ex>n</ex></expan>, wem sie <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> das
                                <expan>befelhe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan>, bey uns zu <expan>empfahe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        und zu in zu <expan>fertig<ex>en</ex></expan>, dem
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>
<expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> zewg <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>. Und
                        ob ir icht <expan>eygensch<ex>aft</ex></expan> erfürt, wo
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> der <expan>r<ex>ömisch</ex></expan> etc. künig
                        yecz <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, so <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schribt</expan> uns
                        das. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>ub</ex></expan> sigillo <expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex>is</expan> Tucher
                                <expan>se<ex>ni</ex><hi rend="sup">oris</hi></expan>
<expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>ist</ex>ri civiu<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica</expan> die <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>festu<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Georii anno etc. xxi.</ab></div>
</div></body>
